  ('medical-tech-moex-06733', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關⽬前臨床上常⽤的HIV檢驗，下列何者錯誤？', '["空窗期⼀般是指病毒抗原偵測不到的時期，平均期間為感染後3個⽉", "臨床實驗室常⽤⻄⽅墨點法（Western blot）作為確認試驗", "⽬前已有⾎清學快篩試劑可區分HIV-1與HIV-2", "可⽤唾液來做篩檢（salivary antibody test）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5103d6329d85", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8b78dcca3f9b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 74, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06734', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於臨床檢驗SARS冠狀病毒（SARS-CoV），下列何者錯誤？', '["⼀般送驗的檢體以⿐咽拭⼦或咽喉拭⼦為主", "病毒亦可以在呼吸道以外的檢體偵測到", "臨床常規性檢驗以病毒培養加上免疫螢光染⾊來做鑑定", "在患者肺部可以偵測到⾼量的細胞激素（cytokines），例如: IL-6、IL-1等"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5103d6329d85", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8b78dcca3f9b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 75, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06735', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於伊波拉病毒（Ebola virus）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["歸類於絲狀病毒科（Filoviridae）", "會引起出⾎熱（hemorrhagic Fever）", "病毒顆粒所帶之基因組為單股正向RNA（single-stranded, positive-sense RNA）", "病毒顆粒表⾯上的glycoprotein（GP）對於結合細胞上之受體（receptor）很重要"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5103d6329d85", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8b78dcca3f9b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 76, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06736', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關狂⽝病毒（rabies virus）的構造與感染，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["狂⽝病毒是桿狀病毒科（Rhabdoviridae）中唯⼀對⼈類具有致病性的病毒", "狂⽝病毒具有單股分節正性RNA基因體（segmented, positive-sense, single-stranded RNA）", "台灣曾在野⽣鼬獾與野⽣錢鼠檢驗出狂⽝病毒", "狂⽝病毒主要在神經元細胞（neuron）中複製病毒顆粒"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5103d6329d85", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8b78dcca3f9b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 77, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
